title: Simple Drawing Tool
date: 2025-12-07
program: draw.bas
screenshot: draw.bmp
description: A basic drawing tool. The brush is a 10x10 pixel square that can be moved around the screen using the arrow keys, enter paints the screen. The colours are selected using the numbers 0-9. Hitting 's' saves the current image as 'draw.bmp' and 'q' quits.
